<div class="min-h-screen bg-background-light text-text-main pb-20">

  <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">

    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-2xl font-medium leading-relaxed pt-10 mb-20">
      座りすぎは喫煙と同等に身体に悪影響を及ぼすとされています<br>
      定期的に立ちあがり健康的な生活を目指しましょう
    </h1>

    <%# How to use %>
    <section class="mb-24">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-primary uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-10">How to use</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 relative">

        <%# ステップ間の矢印（PC） %>
        <div class="hidden md:flex absolute top-1/2 left-[33%] -translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-20 items-center">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary/40 text-4xl">arrow_forward</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden md:flex absolute top-1/2 left-[67%] -translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-20 items-center">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary/40 text-4xl">arrow_forward</span>
        </div>

        <%# STEP 1 %>
        <div class="relative bg-white/70 border border-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center gap-5">
          <div class="text-5xl font-black text-primary/20 absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">01</div>
          <div class="mt-4 w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-5xl">timer</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black mb-2">タイマーをセット</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">好きな時間を選んでスタート。ブラウザを閉じても通知が届きます。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full bg-background-light rounded-2xl p-3 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <div class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs font-bold">60分</div>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary/30 text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
            <div class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary text-white text-xs font-bold shadow-md shadow-primary/20">スタート ▶</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <%# STEP 2 %>
        <div class="relative bg-white/70 border border-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center gap-5">
          <div class="text-5xl font-black text-primary/20 absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">02</div>
          <div class="mt-4 w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-5xl">notifications_active</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black mb-2">通知で休憩のサイン</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">時間になると通知でお知らせ。「休憩する」を押して立ち上がりましょう。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full bg-background-light rounded-2xl p-3">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-left">
              <div class="w-7 h-7 rounded-lg bg-primary flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-sm">notifications</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs font-bold text-text-main">休憩の時間です！</p>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-text-secondary">iStanding</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <%# STEP 3 %>
        <div class="relative bg-white/70 border border-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center gap-5">
          <div class="text-5xl font-black text-primary/20 absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">03</div>
          <div class="mt-4 w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-5xl">fitness_center</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black mb-2">最適な運動を実践</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">運動メニューを提案。完了すると記録され、グラフで継続が見える。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full bg-background-light rounded-2xl p-3 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-700 text-xs font-bold">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">self_improvement</span>ストレッチ
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-xs font-bold">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">fitness_center</span>筋トレ
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-24 bg-white/50 border border-white rounded-[3rem] p-10 md:p-16 shadow-sm">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 text-left">
        <div class="flex-1 space-y-6">
          <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">Push Notification</div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold leading-tight">ブラウザ通知をONにして<br>健康習慣を確実に。</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            このアプリは、ブラウザのプッシュ通知機能を利用します。ログイン後、通知の許可を求めるダイアログが表示されますので、「許可」を選択してください。
            <br><span class="text-sm opacity-70">※スマートフォン・PCの両方に対応しています。</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full max-w-[280px] bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-4 border border-border-light">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">notifications</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="h-2 w-20 bg-gray-200 rounded"></div>
              <div class="h-1.5 w-12 bg-gray-100 rounded mt-1"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">休憩の時間です！</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-text-secondary italic">「立ち上がって肩甲骨を回しましょう」</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-24">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-text-secondary uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-12">The Risks</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left">
        <div class="bg-input-bg-light border border-border-light rounded-2xl p-8">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-4">chair</span>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-3 text-xl">健康リスクの増大</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">脳梗塞やヘルニア等のリスクを高めるだけでなく、座りすぎは寿命に影響を与えるとされています。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-input-bg-light border border-border-light rounded-2xl p-8">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-4">timer</span>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-3 text-xl">集中力の低下</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">血流が滞ることで脳への酸素供給が減り、作業効率が低下。定期的な離席が生産性を高めます。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-input-bg-light border border-border-light rounded-2xl p-8">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-4">monitor_heart</span>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-3 text-xl">専門家による監修</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">理学療法士の知見に基づき、座りすぎ解消に最適な運動メニューを提案します。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <%# CTA %>
    <div class="mt-16 pb-20 flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
      <%= link_to "登録して始める",
        new_user_registration_path,
        class: "inline-block w-full max-w-sm px-12 py-5 rounded-full bg-primary text-white text-xl font-bold hover:bg-primary-hover transition shadow-xl shadow-primary/30 active:scale-95" %>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 w-full max-w-sm">
        <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-border-light"></div>
        <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-medium">または</span>
        <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-border-light"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
        <%= button_to "ゲストユーザーとして始める",
            guest_login_path,
            method: :post,
            class: "inline-block w-full max-w-sm px-12 py-4 rounded-full border-2 border-border-light bg-white text-text-main text-lg font-bold hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition active:scale-95 cursor-pointer" %>
        <p class="flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-text-secondary">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">info</span>
          ゲストユーザーの場合は記録が保存されません
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </main>
</div>
